{"tid":2072003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港麻雀問題] 打花有無門清?","createTime":"2020-06-20T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T23:09:44.000Z","uid":199675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e86123b9c05e2aacffd7024ac14fec64d0a8470d","tid":2072003,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"平時同frd打香港牌通常都係做雙色對對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首牌唔靚摸過幾輪就要決定棄糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時想做平糊/無花/門清/自摸 但係啲frd又話打花就無門清?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可唔可以打花又有門清? 咁樣平糊三番起糊嘅機會高啲 唔使下下防守到流局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無花/正花 一番<br />\n平糊 一番<br />\n門滿 一番<br />\n自摸 一番"},{"pid":"cf1fda449b0edd2852e219383537634c09d4de56","tid":2072003,"uid":42079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"5b553713ec1187112a571988119159813639a6b4","tid":2072003,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"其實三/四番好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但有得食又好似好過流局"},{"pid":"d0a02676a62310c0f5cfacd634d1ba8c91b65500","tid":2072003,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1fda449b0edd2852e219383537634c09d4de56","tid":2072003,"uid":42079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:28:23.000Z","msg":"點解嘅?"},{"pid":"89430b901fcdb004eb056cadbde5dcc23769fc43","tid":2072003,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"一般嚟講打花就唔計門前清<br />\n屌你老母又無花又門清咪求其平糊都打出食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8647cb1517032895008f3b102d1f54014774705b","tid":2072003,"uid":311141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86123b9c05e2aacffd7024ac14fec64d0a8470d","t